**Required on OOB completion.** ISO 8601 timestamp recorded when the user completes (approves or rejects) an OOB authentication request.

**Sources:** [cryptographic_operations_specification.md](../specs/cryptographic_operations_specification.md), [oob_notification_protocol_specification.md](../specs/oob_notification_protocol_specification.md)
</details>

