**Sources:** [error_code_catalog_and_response_specification.md](../specs/error_code_catalog_and_response_specification.md)
</details>

<details>
<summary><code>http_status</code> — integer — HTTP status code for REST surface.</summary>

**Required.** Standard HTTP status code (e.g., 400, 401, 403, 404, 500). Used by the operator REST API; MCP surface uses JSON-RPC error codes instead.

**Sources:** [error_code_catalog_and_response_specification.md](../specs/error_code_catalog_and_response_specification.md)
</details>

